data.title: My Secret Fascination with Michel Houellebecq
data.meta_description: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7-Ap1g83Dg4 COUNTERPUNCH WEEKEND EDITION MARCH 27-29, 2015 A Quixotic Longing for a Benign Authority My Secret Fascination with Michel Houellebecq by LOUIS PROYECT I attended the press screening for “The Kidnapping of Michel Houellebecq” with the expectation that I would learn something about the controversial novelist whose name has become synonymous with Islamophobia. Fully expecting…
